•   z,y,x : [ z = m.n ∧ y = g.n ∧ x = h.n
            , z = m.(n+1) ∧ y = g.(n+1) ∧ x = h.(n+1)
            ]

=   Focus on postcondition

    •   z = m.(n+1) ∧ y = g.(n+1)

    ≡   Definition of m

        z = m.n ↑ g.(n+1) ∧ y = g.(n+1)

    ≡   Substitution

        z = m.n ↑ y ∧ y = g.(n+1)

    ■

⋯   z,y,x : [ z = m.n ∧ y = g.n ∧ x = h.n
            , z = m.n ↑ y ∧ y = g.(n+1) ∧ x = h.(n+1)
            ]

■